title: Should Enzyme Sponsor ETHGlobal ETHOnline?
body:
Recently we sponsored the ETHGlobal Hack.money hackathon and saw good submissions. Between Sept 17 - Oct 15, there is the EthGlobal ETHOnline hackathon.

This vote relates to sponsoring that hackathon as well.

Cost to Council: $18K + Prizes $2-3k each

Benefits  of this tier:

- Dedicated channel in the online event community
- Community advertisement post-event
- 2 online community announcements (sent to the whole community) ideal for announcing Sulu release.
- 45 seconds to present our prize in the kick-off (pre-recorded session)
- Up to 3 winners can be selected (max prize being 8K)
- Sponsor prize workshop session of 30 minutes.
